%p 
  Hi 
  = "#{@employee.full_name}," 
  %br
  Until today 
  = Time.now.strftime('%m/%d/%Y')
  you have: 
  %h3
    = @employee.total_vacations_days
    Vacations days available
  %h4 Here is the detailed table of all your requests  
  %table
    %tr
      %th Description
      %th Days
      %th Requested on
      %th Status
    - @vacations.each do |vacation|
      %tr
        %td= vacation.description
        %td= vacation.days
        %td= vacation.requested_on
        %td= vacation.status_name
%p
  If you have any additional question please let us know.
  %br
  %br
  Thanks,
  %br
  Human Resources Department